title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H3 – Sep 29 2022
itunes:title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H3 – Sep 29 2022
description:
Clay and Buck listen in on Governor DeSantis' press briefing on Hurricane Ian. Delray Beach caller loves Lee Zeldin. Republicans in blue states have a shot if conservatives turn out. Libs of TikTok's Chaya Raichik talks to C&B about why she's such a threat to Big Tech and the left. Clay and Buck prep for a big night in NYC. Nord Stream whodunit: If John Brennan says it was Russia, it probably wasn't Russia.
